Detailed Description

cvmx_fpa_pool::_threshold

FPA_POOLX_THRESHOLD = FPA's Pool 0-7 Threshold When the value of FPA_QUEX_AVAILABLE is equal to FPA_POOLX_THRESHOLD[THRESH] when a pointer is allocated or deallocated, set interrupt FPA_INT_SUM[POOLXTH].
